869.question: What is the state of the art system mentioned?

4-Table3-1.png: The state-of-the-art system mentioned in the image is the one developed by Raganato et al. (2017b) for fine-grained English all-words WSD on the test sets, which achieved an F1-score of 85.5%.

869.answer:
Two knowledge-based systems,
two traditional word expert supervised systems, six recent neural-based systems, and one BERT feature-based system.
